{
  "stem": "14060.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 453.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We heard already cannon fire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, the sounds were getting near, so we knew any minute it can happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I didn't feel that strong anymore that I should go on the march or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We knew about the marches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all I did was create a passive resistance, which consisted of nothing else, but as they pushed us, I just sat down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I sat down there whether there was mud, water, or a stone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I just sort of collapsed on the-- I sat down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So eventually, while we're still on the bottom camp, two people picked up my arm, and suddenly somebody with a big stick, a heavy timber stick which, they had, hit me over the head.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought my head splits, but nothing serious happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't even bleed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if I did, I didn't notice it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I walked another few steps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By that time, I was through the barbed wire gates which separated the middle camp from the lower-- the zeltlager, the tent camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said down again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somehow or other, one of these non-Jewish German political-- either Socialist or Communist-- seemed to have taken pity on me or something and said to me in German, [GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What's wrong with you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I answered him, ich kann night gehen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I can't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He picked me up, moved me out of the line, which was totally against the rules and regulation, put me in front of block 59 on a heap of dead people, and he said two words to me-- [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Oh, three words, actually.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[GERMAN] And with that, the man turned around and he went back and stood in the line.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because I looked up what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These 5,000 people were taken out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
